    <published>2024-06-02T01:45:18.000Z</published>
    <updated>2024-06-02T01:55:09.281Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><p>就读于某升学学校的女子高中生白石紬希(しらいしつむぎ)只是漠然地想着“好想死”。</p><p>不论学习还是运动，紬希都处于平均以下。<br>无论梦想还是目标抑或是想做的事，紬希都没有。<br>尽管如此，成年人们仍然告诉她“为了未来而努力是值得的”，于是她开始朝着看不见的『未来』努力奔跑。<br>因此，她所能做的只有为了取得好成绩而努力学习。</p><p>然而，她在面临一个关乎未来发展的重要模拟考试时，犯了一个大错…</p><p><img src="https://r2.touchgal.net/2023/10/20231024185546654-RJ01012429_img_smp5-1024x576.jpg"></img></p><hr><a class="btn-beautify " href="http://111.173.104.54:5244/d/%E5%8D%97%2B6TBgal%E5%90%88%E9%9B%86%EF%BC%8C%E8%A7%A3%E5%8E%8B%E7%A0%81south-plus/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E8%BD%AE%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0-%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86/%E6%9C%AC%E4%BD%93/%5B%E3%82%AA%E3%83%BC%E3%83%90%E3%83%BC%E3%83%95%E3%83%AD%E3%82%A6%5D%20%E3%81%82%E3%81%97%E3%81%9F%E3%80%81%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F(%E3%81%84%E3%81%AE%E3%81%A1)%E3%81%8C%E7%B5%82%E3%82%8F%E3%82%8B%E3%81%A8%E3%81%97%E3%81%9F%E3%82%89%20%20%E8%8B%A5%E7%94%9F%E5%91%BD%E4%BA%8E%E6%98%8E%E6%97%A5%E8%90%BD%E5%B9%95%20%E6%B1%89%E5%8C%96%E7%A1%AC%E7%9B%98%E7%89%88%5B%E6%94%BE%E6%89%8B%E6%97%B6%E7%9A%84%E5%BF%83%E5%8A%A8%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E6%B1%89%E5%8C%96%5D/%5B%E3%82%AA%E3%83%BC%E3%83%90%E3%83%BC%E3%83%95%E3%83%AD%E3%82%A6%5D%20%E3%81%82%E3%81%97%E3%81%9F%E3%80%81%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F(%E3%81%84%E3%81%AE%E3%81%A1)%E3%81%8C%E7%B5%82%E3%82%8F%E3%82%8B%E3%81%A8%E3%81%97%E3%81%9F%E3%82%89%20%20%E8%8B%A5%E7%94%9F%E5%91%BD%E4%BA%8E%E6%98%8E%E6%97%A5%E8%90%BD%E5%B9%95%20%E6%B1%89%E5%8C%96%E7%A1%AC%E7%9B%98%E7%89%88%5B%E6%94%BE%E6%89%8B%E6%97%B6%E7%9A%84%E5%BF%83%E5%8A%A8%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E6%B1%89%E5%8C%96%5D.rar"   title="点击下载"><i class="red larger"></i><span>点击下载</span></a><span class="hide-inline"><button type="button" class="hide-button" style="background-color: #FF7242;color: #fff">查看隐藏内容  </button><span class="hide-content">解压码south-plus</span></span>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
